This article describes the setup of an Intel Core 2 Solo/Duo/Quad processor.

The Intel Core 2 line of processors supports both the 32-bit and 64-bit mode. The general pros and cons can be read about in the [[Wikipedia:64-bit#32-bit_vs_64-bit|Wikipedia article]]. By now only very few applications do not support 64-bit mode or work in a 32-bit compatibility mode.

